Subjects: BiographyJudgesLawyersPublic officialsUNC PressAuthors: Stumpf, Vernon O. Origin - location: Chowan CountyEdentonFrom: Dictionary of North Carolina Biography, University of North Carolina Press. 
		1 January 1988 | Stumpf, Vernon O. 		

